videos.headline: Penn State's Thomas nearly takes back 99-yard return
videos.description: Penn State kick returner Johnathan Thomas dices through Indiana tacklers on a 95-yard kick return, but runs out of real estate as he steps out of bounds before the goal line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State's Thomas nearly takes back 99-yard return) 2018/10/20

videos.headline: Indiana RB fully extends for TD
videos.description: Indiana puts a bow on an 81-yard touchdown drive as running back Stevie Scott takes the triple-option hand off and stretches to the goal line for a 3-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Indiana RB fully extends for TD) 2018/10/12
